Text: This looks like a great show, if only I could get those final kilobytes. Woe is me.

Mr. Green Panther, I am totally green too. I am your friend. I love you. I am very close to completing my download of your fine, fine, superfine torrent. Less than 20MB to go my friend. Did I mention how much I love you? It's real my friend. Anyhow...this is such an excellent period for FZ concerts, I was wondering could you give me those last MBytes I so desperately need and crave my friend. Regardless, I will always love you forever, Green Panther, you wonderful being.
